text: Imgflip is an Internet meme generating website that allows users to create memes using Artificial Intelligence, text, animated GIF files, images, videos and other digital mediums. Imgflip is owned by Crunchbase which describe imgflip as "an online website for creating and sharing images. It is specialized in memes and GIFs" ==References== Category:Internet memes Category:Artificial intelligence Category:American websites
